"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Watching a few good podcasts and reading articles focused on crypto eventually leads to overwhelm. I actually quit for a few months - 8 - and when I came back I saw that many had done the same. Burn out is common and I still havenâ€™t figured out how to avoid it. I may be walking the same path I did 2 years ago and moving towards the same end.\\n\\nWhat I keep telling myself is that I need to choose an area. That is the solution I have set upon. Choose a field, a chain, a topic, and focus on that. This, I think, will cut down on the information overload and on the disorientation of trying to be up to date, knowledgeable and capable of action in every fricken crypto domain. Focus.\\n\\nThis then is my strategy.\",\"timestamp\":1636289255,\"title\":\"Crypto Overwhelm\"},\"digest\":\"vVDTwxnM5LA6-EM0aTRCjYUpKVHXA8vo3JsqW2vCxos\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x8351076a6A1F4524c6e0Af574A299A3051B58724\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ZU24ynHcTI1po4eTQ75nsp_AQTHdC4ms4PPHcQpaVlk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"9AfnEFdIU69s3s_fEa16YTEWtpFOCX9nZ4MhZkRNvJM\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"VZ01Syr9VZRe9C2NDgckGNryrOyA1QRHrdSz91ugym3604KkxLwb5fuj3WvrilTUPwXJ1rhGzWKG3VII5D_cvw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x69d55f16959ad1d9efd7cc8c4154c61397e6c3af3b34e45775564cdcf9fc9c533a34771f98e92b5657b89811faf80207d0313c3c5b1e320759764249cfda21cb1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ZU24ynHcTI1po4eTQ75nsp_AQTHdC4ms4PPHcQpaVlk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"9AfnEFdIU69s3s_fEa16YTEWtpFOCX9nZ4MhZkRNvJM\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"vVDTwxnM5LA6-EM0aTRCjYUpKVHXA8vo3JsqW2vCxos\"}"